ives.gov.uk/education/medieval/magna-carta/","urlTitle":"National Archives - Magna Carta","jurisdictionLevel":2},{"id":1705188,"age":38,"year":"1224","julianDay":2168117,"title":"France Declares War on England","description":"France declared war on England as Louis VIII of France attacked Poitou and northern Gascony.","jurisdictionLevel":2},{"id":1705189,"age":73,"year":"1259","julianDay":2180901,"title":"100 Years of Conflict Between England and France Ends","description":"Treaty of Paris was signed on December 4, 1259, which ended 100 years of conflict between England and France.","url":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Treaty_of_Paris_(1259)","urlTitle":"Wikipedia - Treaty of Paris 1259","jurisdictionLevel":2}],"lifeSummary":"Lord Matthew Ridiche married Agnes Rediche before 1278, in Reddish, Lancashire, England. They were the parents of at least 1 daughter. He died before 1306, in Reddish, Lancashire, England."},"et":{"–bef 1306":"–enne 1306","–1306":"–1306","1164–Female":"1164–Surnud","1259":"1259","1215":"1215","1224":"1224","before 1278":"enne 1278","bef 1306":"enne 1306","1164":"1164","about 1164":"umbes 1164","1306":"1306","Little Hulton, Lancashire, England":"Little Hulton, Lancashire, England","Reddish, Lancashire, England":"Reddish, Lancashire, England"},"fi":{"–bef 1306":"–ennen vuotta 1306","–1306":"–1306","1164–Female":"1164–Kuollut","1259":"1259","1215":"1215","1224":"1224","before 1278":"ennen vuotta 1278","bef 1306":"ennen vuotta 1306","1164":"1164","about 1164":"noin 1164","1306":"1306","Little Hulton, Lancashire, England":"Little Hulton, Lancashire, England","Reddish, Lancashire, England":"Reddish, Lancashire, England"},"fr":{"–bef 1306":"–avant 1306","–1306":"–1306","1164–Female":"1164–Décédée","1259":"1259","1215":"1215","1224":"1224","before 1278":"avant 1278","bef 1306":"avant 1306","1164":"1164","about 1164":"environ 1164","1306":"1306","Little Hulton, Lancashire, England":"Little Hulton, Lancashire, Angleterre","Reddish, Lancashire, England":"